================================================================================
ATTRIBUTION & PROVENANCE
================================================================================

This repository (ign-solutions-io/ai-skills) is a fork (clone) of
mattpocock/skills — "Skills For Real Engineers" by Matt Pocock
(https://github.com/mattpocock/skills). The substantial majority of the skills
here are Matt Pocock's original work, carried over from that upstream repository
and used under the MIT License above. All credit for them remains with him.

To remove any possible confusion about who authored what, the provenance of
every skill is recorded below. Any skill NOT listed under "Additions made in
this fork" originates from Matt Pocock's upstream repository.

Matt Pocock's original skills (from the upstream repository)
------------------------------------------------------------
engineering/  diagnose, grill-with-docs, improve-codebase-architecture,
              prototype, setup-ai-skills (named "setup-matt-pocock-skills"
              upstream; renamed in this fork), tdd, to-issues, to-prd, triage,
              zoom-out
productivity/ caveman, grill-me, handoff, write-a-skill
misc/         git-guardrails-claude-code, migrate-to-shoehorn,
              scaffold-exercises, setup-pre-commit
personal/     edit-article, obsidian-vault
in-progress/  review, teach, writing-beats, writing-fragments, writing-shape
deprecated/   design-an-interface, qa, request-refactor-plan,
              ubiquitous-language

Additions made in this fork (NOT from the upstream repository)
--------------------------------------------------------------
productivity/pressure-test  Original work by Zaprin Ignatiev (ziroock).
productivity/pass           Added in this fork by Zaprin Ignatiev (ziroock).
productivity/andrey-k       Curated by Zaprin Ignatiev (ziroock) from Andrej
                            Karpathy's publicly shared guidelines on LLM coding
                            pitfalls; not an original work of either author.
